                div.o-grid--3-5.o-grid--1-1-on-800
                    h2.c-section__title Social Media Monitoring
                    p This tool allows you to find out how many times a specified URL was shared across various social media platforms, including Facebook, LinkedIn, Google+, Pinterest, Twitter, VK and more. Want stats on a large number of links? Our Bulk URL Importer makes it easy to grab social media data across many URLs in one go.
