                div.o-grid--3-5.o-grid--1-1-on-800
                    h2.c-section__title Our Data Source
                    p We source data straight from the official APIs for each social media service, along with Twitter engagement data pulled from newsharecounts.com. Using quality data, you can be sure MarketingTool is yielding accurate and current results. 

            section.c-section.c-section--text.o-grid.o-grid--middle: div.o-gutters--80.o-gutters--25-on-800
                div.o-grid--3-5.o-grid--1-1-on-800
                    h2.c-section__title Single vs Multi URL
                    p Whether you want to pull up the social stats for one URL or multiple URLs at once, this tool offers the flexibility to handle your single or bulk input needs. 
